Package parser.LogicScripter

Class UtilityKeywordTypeMatcher

java.lang.Object
parser.LogicScripter.UtilityKeywordTypeMatcher
public class UtilityKeywordTypeMatcher
extends java.lang.Object
Utility KeywordPatterns Type Matcher is a helper class that provides matchers to words from the keywords patterns json schema. This contains a compiled list a keywords used in the JSON and their corresponding regexes and matcher functions.
